</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Sorry I think this is so new that there does not seem to be another thread about this.<br />
<br />
I have my Adventure Stone in my PoP Charm.  I figured since they both can be replaced I would tinker with these two.  I found the bird bath and the augmentation went as advertised, but I have hear at least 5 different version of how this Adventure Stone is supposed to gain in power.<br />
<br />
I have heard that:<br />
<br />
You have to get five bits of lore from one theme.  You get one bit of lore for every 2 wins in a theme and you must hail an NPC in the camp of that theme.  I have 7 wins in MM and I have notice nothing from hailing the NPCs in BB.<br />
<br />
I have heard that you must have 2 wins per theme to get the first upgrade to adventure stone.<br />
<br />
I have heard that you can mix and match wins for lore after your first 10 wins.  I am assuming this has to be 10 at one theme or 2 at each since I have had not mention of lore or stories from any NPCs.<br />
<br />
Thanks in advance for clearing up my confussion.<br />
<br />
Sion</p>
	
	
	
	
	
