	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>The NPCs in the camps are easy to find. They are in the wayfarer camps, they are not the magi, and they do not have other functions.<br />
<br />
That eliminates the raid recruiters, adventure recruiters, adventure merchants, soulbinder, and magus. Should only leave a handful of NPCs at the camp. Hail them all. You know the right one when you get a message that says either you gain new information, or you need to adventure for more information.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
		<div class="smallfont"><a href="report.php?s=685a16cd04b32288b8f1b5c352dbdf17&amp;postid=181691">Report Post</a> | IP: <a href="postings.php?s=685a16cd04b32288b8f1b5c352dbdf17&amp;do=getip&postid=181691">Logged</a></div>
	
