	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Just go back to the camps you didnt get all your hails done at, find the NPC that does that, and hail them until they tell you that you need to adventure more. <br />
<br />
Sometimes, they will also tell you to go talk to other NPCs that are NOT located in the camps. Normally, those NPCs are located in an adjacent zone, and you pretty much need a tracker to find them the first time. One of these is in WFP, near the PoK book.</p>
	
	
	
